==Plants==
* &quot;Aconitum&quot;, a genus of toxic flowering plants of the northern hemisphere
** &quot;Aconitum lycoctonum&quot; or northern wolfsbane
* &quot;Arnica montana&quot;, a toxic European flowering plant

