===The Lagrange inversion formula===

As mentioned above, any formal series formula_340 with &quot;f&quot;0 = 0 and &quot;f&quot;1 ≠ 0 has a composition inverse formula_341 The following relation between the coefficients of &quot;gn&quot; and &quot;f&quot;−&quot;k&quot; holds (&quot;&quot;):

